OOC:That's cool Yanshosh. I understand. I'll just have hem get real 
drunk and stumble around the Alliance base. As for how I know it's 
Bob Skir, I went to www.bobskir.com, which is an actual website where 
you can e-mail him questions. I'll put that up on the links in a sec. 
But I told him about our anniversary and everything, and than he e-
mailed me back saying he would love to go but had to check with 
mainframe and people about making this appearance, even if it is by 
computer. He'll e-nail me back in a few days.

Prebon

Prebon laughed at the demand.

"No way! Your little army out numbers the one I have with me. I 
cannot form Tamron because I have left two bots behind. As soon as I 
give you Spears you will track me down to my base and attack so you 
can get Striker. Well I don't think so. As long as their life is in 
danger you will not attack me. One on one, one sector over here. A 
holo-map for two prisoners that could've been mine. I think you have 
pretty good deal there. Meet me ther in 2 mega cycles. Come alone. I 
will."
